Action: file_editor str_replace /app/backend/server.py --old-str "def on_mqtt_disconnect(client, userdata, rc, properties=None):
    logger.warning(f\"Disconnected from MQTT broker, rc: {rc}\")" --new-str "def on_mqtt_disconnect(client, userdata, disconnect_flags, rc, properties=None):
    logger.warning(f\"Disconnected from MQTT broker, rc: {rc}\")"
