  The icons have different naming. Let me use WifiHigh instead:
Action: file_editor str_replace /app/frontend/src/App.js --old-str "import { Broadcast, Activity, Cpu, Wifi, WifiOff, PaperPlaneTilt, Terminal, List, Crosshair, Drone } from \"@phosphor-icons/react\";" --new-str "import { Broadcast, Activity, Cpu, WifiHigh, WifiSlash, PaperPlaneTilt, Terminal, List, Crosshair, Drone } from \"@phosphor-icons/react\";"
